=1534317170"},{"id":704588,"node":"宽带症候群","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1594743650","description":"<p>北京联通 300M 。\n看到移动宽带很便宜，考虑要不要再拉一条……不过再拉一条有什么用呢？该怎么用呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/704588","replies":39,"created_ts":1599355547,"created":"09:25:47","title":"有了联通宽带之后，再拉一条移动的有用吗？","author":"whileFalse","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/whileFalse","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c0b4d3bc97c297b9ad044ba06c42d94e?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":704687,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1594743680","description":"<p>比微博还要无耻的“喂你吃屎”型广告轰炸</p>\n<p>我 Intel 10th I5 处理器加 16G DDR4 的机器加固态硬盘，打开软件仍然有卡顿现象。</p>\n<p>现在是不是只能用这个东西下软件了？我不是搞技术的，下一些美剧和电影或者磁力链接是不是只能用这坨屎？之前朋友推荐了一个，完全没有资源，各位老哥有什么替代的方案吗？</p>\n<p>还是说这玩意就跟微信一样，已经处于生态垄断，在国内完全为所欲为的状态了？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/704687","replies":38,"created_ts":1599400946,"created":"22:02:26","title":"天下是否苦迅雷久矣？","author":"xzlzy","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xzlzy","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/456d0bd30cb7650f0677854db48d1bac?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":704645,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1583044904","description":"准备采购正版 win10，看到网上说的一般买个十几套就行，，现在公司在用电脑有 70-80 台，那买多少个 win 授权呢，，一套查到价格 1800 元。。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/704645","replies":38,"created_ts":1599379314,"created":"16:01:54","title":"公司 100 多人，该买多少套正版 WIN10？有没行规？","author":"lakie","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lakie","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9aee7fa889ebbe035ee3be35df4f594f?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":704581,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1599144047","description":"<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/AivWpbLHl8-Qh_NWq5Cbrw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/AivWpbLHl8-Qh_NWq5Cbrw</a><br /><br />我我实名反对无脑微服务快 4 年了。4 年里无数人教我做人的道理。<br /><br />但是没有一个说得出所谓维服务之解决了 ci/cd 的问题外什么问题。<br /><br />终于风向要变了。<br /><br />我曾经在某位阿里恰饭微服务大佬的群里和他们吵了三天最后被几个连班都没上过的门徒硬是辱骂出群。<br /><br />将来会证实的这波微服务和几年前的 openstack 一样都是历史的耻辱柱。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/704581","replies":35,"created_ts":1599351583,"created":"08:19:43","title":"看来风向要变了，终于有公司敢不吹 docker 和微服务了《王者荣耀为什么不使用微服务架构？》","author":"594duck","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/594duck","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a1a3/e172/12314_mini.png?m=1355716739"},{"id":704599,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1590337894","description":"<p>不会出现 boom 的情况吧</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>周边没有维修店😅 得回到大城市了 才能维修 😅</p>\n<p><img alt=\"1wH8KFE\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1wH8KFE.png\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/704599","replies":30,"created_ts":1599359569,"created":"10:32:49","title":"苹果本鼓包了 D 面被撑开了~ 还能继续使用吗 😅","author":"justin2018","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/justin2018","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/83e8/4827/351542_mini.png?m=1547034280"},{"id":704591,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1594743680","description":"<p>工作中发现有一类人，技术明明很菜，但是态度很强硬；\n如果工作中自己的缺陷不肯承认，让别人去适配自己，出了问题甩锅给别人，有没有碰到过？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/704591","replies":24,"created_ts":1599357202,"created":"09:53:22","title":"有没有见过那种又菜，又凶的人？","author":"doudou1523102","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/doudou1523102","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f7f8/68d2/434450_mini.png?m=1572166746"}]